---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Rahul Kulkarni. AI enthusiast with a consulting core."
  activeNav="about"
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">About</div>
      <h1>
        Healthcare enthusiast. <span class="italic">AI-powered.</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding-top: 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 760px;">
        <p style="font-size: 1.15rem;">
          I'm Rahul Kulkarni — an AI enthusiast with a consulting core. My work has covered the full sweep of healthcare commercial — analytics, operations, strategy.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
          The work taught me three things.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-num">01</div>
            <h3>Pharma follows patterns.</h3>
            <p>Patient experience, HCP behaviour, treatment paradigms, field strategy, payer dynamics. Weeks to learn, months to shape. AI compresses that arc.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-num">02</div>
            <h3>Speed beats precision.</h3>
            <p>In most decisions, speed outperforms accuracy. Pulling data, structuring decks, chasing references — necessary, but shouldn't eat your time-to-decision.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-num">03</div>
            <h3>Reimagine, don't replace.</h3>
            <p>Faster decisions come from reimagining traditional workflows — AI in the right places, humans where they matter most.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 4rem;">What I built</h2>

        <p>
          Built end to end in 12 hours. Two applications, live and free. The site itself is the proof — of a discipline I'm working on: <em>think fast, act faster</em>. Less time talking about AI. More time acting with it.
        </p>

        <p>
          If something here sparks an idea — for your own work, for a workflow you'd like to see, for a problem you've been thinking about — let's chat.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tight">
    <div class="content" style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="mailto:raulkulkarni@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
